@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jurqvy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.53 + 0.82)
    v2 = (0.71 * wp.sin(0.60))
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v0 + 0.98)) - wp.abs((v1 + 0.11 * v0 + 0.81)))
    tmp = wp.exp(((v0 + 0.08 + tmp + 0.02) - (v0 + 0.71 / v2 + 0.99)))
    data[tid] = v0
